From cou.: 11 The testing approaches discussed for reversible reactions can hence be applied straight to simulations that are based on Nernstian boundary conditions, as these conditions exclusively describe reversible processes. In addition to that, presented methods can be employed to validate simulations that use other kinetic models, if boundary conditions are calculated in certain limits.
From Soup: 11 The testing approaches discussed for reversible reactions can hence be applied straight to simulations that are based on Nernstian boundary conditions, as these conditions exclusively describe reversible processes. In addition to that, presented methods can be employed to validate simulations that use other kinetic models, if boundary conditions are calculated in certain limits.
