From Soup: 62 With this work, we aim to points out the difficulty as well as the necessity of rigorous software testing and provide a general guide to testing electrochemical simulation software as well as a tool set to validate simulations of common models. To this end, we discuss the testing process of electrochemical simulation software for the modelling of electrochemically-reversible two-species systems with respect to the one- and two-dimensional cases of a macro- and a micro-disk electrode, respectively.
